&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of working as a Liveops Manager in a game with a strong liveops cadence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze current monetization strategy including pricing, segmentation, what value we give to users and define the right strategy for the game&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Frame hypotheses, design A/B tests and translate insights into high-impact product decisions, going from idea to live experiments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong quantitative and analytical skills with ability to monitor, analyze key performance metrics (average revenue per user, conversion, funnel, churn) and drive metrics-driven decision making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop best practices to drive operational excellence in a live-ops team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with features team to ensure live-ops needs are communicated and planned while new features are being developed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
