&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of working as a Liveops Manager in a game with a strong liveops cadence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Worked in a volatile and fast-paced environment and not afraid to adapt to changes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good communication skills and experience aligning with stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
